{Speech 21 Answer Exit}{}{Got it, thanks for the answer. Bye!}
{Speech 22}{}{I want to explore the sea route to China. They say that if you sail far, far to the West, sooner or later you'll run into land. I've also heard that the Earth is a sphere, and in time you can even come back to where you started from. I don't know if it's true.}
{Speech 22 Answer 18}{}{Wow. I wanted to ask one more thing...}
{Speech 22 Answer Exit}{}{Well, good luck on your travels!}
